title: Kangana Ranaut’s Pant Suit Is Sexier Than Any You’ve Seen Before
text:
A post shared by Ami Patel (@stylebyami) on Feb 20, 2017 at 11:55pm PST 
Kangana Ranaut stepped out for the promotions of Rangoon looking excessively sexy. And why are we not surprised! Celebrity stylist Ami Patel styled her in a 3 piece pantsuit from H&M with the inner waistcoat as worn as a bustier. With her hair styled in a retro wave, celebrity hair and makeup artist opted for bright red lips and thick eyeliner. A post shared by Sanjay Kumar Dauhaliya (@shnoy09) on Feb 21, 2017 at 12:29am PST 
Kangana’s look is perfect for any girl who wants to up her style game. Are you finding her as sexy as we are. Share your views on her look by commenting below. 0
